javax.accessibility.Accessible, java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.util.EventListener, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.WindowConstants
public class DialogCheckEnregistrement
extends javax.swing.JDialog
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener

DialogCheckEnregistrement will display the Enregistrement and those which are close to it and ask for confirmation.

Return true or false to askOk Buttons : Ok : confirm Enregistrement and return true.
Cancel : return false
